{
  "chapter": 52,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十二回\"陷阱\"，李寻欢追寻铁传甲下落时遇到一名乞丐，该乞丐自称不认识铁传甲，却在骗取李寻欢银子后突然出手，以沾衣十八跌、七十二路擒拿手、分筋错骨手和塞外摔跌四种绝技将李寻欢摔倒在地。随后瞎子、独眼妇人、青衣大汉、卖臭豆干的小贩等同党现身，揭露这从头到尾都是精心设计的圈套。瞎子透露主谋另有其人，将李寻欢带到龙啸云府上。龙啸云假意热情款待，实则设局诱捕李寻欢以引来铁传甲。胡不归虽帮龙啸云做事却深感愧疚，自认不是东西。龙小云趁乱想偷袭李寻欢报仇，被龙啸云当众掌掴并斥责。胡不归最终忍无可忍，大骂龙啸云父子不是东西后愤然离去。本章揭示龙啸云的阴险面目，为后续剧情埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我什么人也不认得，什么人也不认得我，我一个人也不认得，一个人也不认得我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你这人想干什么？想抢我的银子？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不得了，不得了，有强盗在抢银子呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "快把银子还给我，不然我跟你拼命。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "只要你回答我几句话，我不但将这点银子还给你，还送你一锭大的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，你要问我什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "你可是铁传甲的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我没有朋友……穷要饭的都没有朋友。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "那么，你为何要帮他的忙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "谁的忙我也不帮，谁也没帮过我的忙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "你今天难道没有见到过一个身材很高大，皮肤很黑，脸上长着络腮大胡子的人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我好像看到过一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "你在哪里看到他的？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "在茅房里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "茅房？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "茅房就是大便的地方，我正在大便，那小子忽然闯了进来，问我想不想赚几斤酒喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "谁不想赚几斤酒喝。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但我看那小子穿得比我还破烂，哪里像有钱买酒给我喝的样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "越有钱的人，越喜欢装穷，这道理你不明白？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "一点也不错，那小子果然有锭银子，而且还给我看了，我就问他要我怎么样才能赚得到这锭银子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "他怎么说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我以为他一定有什么稀奇古怪的花样，谁知他只是要我跟他换套衣服，然后低着头走出去，千万不要抬头。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "这银子赚得倒真容易。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "是呀，所以我看那小子一定有毛病。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "我也有毛病，我的银子比他的更好赚。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "只要你能带我找到那有毛病的小子，我就将这些银子都给你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，我带你去，但银子你却一定要先给我。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我看你这银子一定是偷来的，否则怎会如此轻易就送人？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你为什么不说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "阁下的脖子若被人扼住，还有什么话好说？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "若有人暗算了我，又扼住了我的脖子，我一定要将他祖宗八代都骂出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "我眼睛并没有瞎，却未看出阁下是身怀绝技的武林高手，要骂也只能骂我自己。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你果然是个怪人，像你这样的怪人我倒未见过……你再说两句，就只怕要脸红了！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "乞丐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人不但是个君子，而且还是个好人，这种人我一向最吃不消，你们再不出来，我可不管了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "妙计妙计，佩服佩服。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "原来这件事根本就和铁传甲全无关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "关系是有的，只不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只不过我从来未曾见过铁传甲，也不知道他是何许人也，方才找他们演了那出戏，完全是为了要你看的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "那倒的确是出好戏。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "戏倒的确是出好戏，否则又怎能叫李探花上当？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "原来各位非但早就知道我是谁了，而且还早已见到了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "阁下还未入城，已有人见到了阁下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "各位怎会认得我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "在下等虽不认得你，却有人认得你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "各位既然不认得我，为何对我如此照顾？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为的就是铁传甲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "在下等对他都想念得很，只苦于找不到他，但他若知道李探花也和在下等在一起，就会不远千里而来与我等相见了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "他若不来呢？各位岂非白费了心机？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他的事你绝不会不管，你的事他也绝不会置之不理，两位的关系，在下等早已清楚得很，否则又怎会定下此计？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "阁下能想得出这样的妙计，倒也真不容易。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "在下若有如此智谋，这双眼睛只怕也就不会瞎了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "定计的人不是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "也不是我，我脑袋一向有毛病，一想到要害人，就会头疼。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "原来各位幕后还另有主谋之人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你也用不着问他是谁，反正你总会见着他的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你见着他时，也许就会觉得活在世上根本就是多余的，不如还是早些死了的好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位已将我那兄弟请来了么？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "在下等幸不辱命，总算已将李探花请来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "一别又是两年，兄弟你可想煞大哥我了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大哥若是想见我，只要吩咐一声，我立刻就到，又何必劳动这么多朋友的大驾呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "说得好，说得好，连我的脸都被你说红了，听了这话能面不改色的人，我真是佩服得很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我早已算准了兄弟你一定会来，早已准备好接风的酒，你我兄弟多年不见，这次可得痛痛快快地喝几杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位快请入座，请，请。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "各位难道不肯赏光么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "在下等答应龙大爷做这件事，为的完全是铁传甲，如今在下等任务已了，等那铁传甲来时，只望龙大爷莫要忘记通知一声。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "至于龙大爷的酒，在下等万万不敢叨扰，龙大爷这样的朋友，在下等也是万万高攀不上的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "老实说，我本来也想走的，但放着这么好的酒菜，不吃岂非可惜？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你也喝一杯吧，这种人的酒你不喝也是白不喝，喝了也是白喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这位胡大侠，兄弟你只怕还不认得……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "胡大侠？台甫莫非是不归二字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "一点也不错，胡不归就是我！你嘴里虽称我胡大侠，心里一定在想：哦，原来这人就是胡疯子，难怪做事说话都有些疯疯癫癫的……是不是？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，你这人有意思，看来只怕也是个疯子……你若不疯，也不会跟龙啸云这样的人交上朋友了，是不是？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "但你千万莫要以为我也是他的朋友，我帮他这次忙，只因为我欠过他的情，这件事做完，我和他就再也没有半点关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过这件事做得实在有欠光明，实在丢人，实在差劲，实在不是东西，实在混账已极……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "text": "无论如何，胡兄最后那出手一击，我纵有防备，也是万万闪避不开的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "放屁放屁，简直是放屁，我若不用奸计，哪里能沾得着你，我害了你，你反来安慰我，你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这人神魂不定，喜怒无常，黑白不分，颠三倒四，说哭就哭，说笑就笑，实在他妈的不是东西。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "但你却比我更不是东西，你儿子比你还不是东西，他明明有两条腿，却要学狗在地上爬，难道想在桌子下面捡骨头吃么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大丈夫恩怨分明，这句话你老人家说对不对？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "自然是对的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "江湖英雄讲究的也是有仇必报，有恩必偿，他废去了孩儿一身武功，令孩儿终生残废，孩儿想要他两条腿，也是天经地义的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "你想复仇，是么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "但你可知道他是谁么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我只知道他是我的仇人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "但你可知他是你父亲的八拜之交？他无论怎么教训你，都是应该的，你怎可对他有复仇之心？怎敢对他无礼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "侄儿已知道错了，侄儿年纪还小，李大叔千万莫要和侄儿一般见识，就饶了侄儿这一次吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡不归",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这父子两人我实在受不了，我想吐，想吐……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 385
    }
